description:
In this karaoke video, I'm singing "Karaoke w Lyrics" using the key of C. If you're looking for a fun and easy way to worship God, then this is the video for you!

Whether you're a seasoned worship leader or a beginner, this karaoke video is perfect for you! In addition to the gospel song, I'll also teach you some helpful tips on how to karaoke effectively. So be sure to check it out!

Title: Blessed Assurance
Author: Fanny Crosby
Music performed by C Lalhmuaka, 3 Sisters  youtube production!
